143
00:14:18,239 --> 00:14:20,833
I've got a ticket here for a train
that leaves at 3:00 a.m.

144
00:14:20,959 --> 00:14:24,076
Gets me to San Francisco just in time
to catch the next boat for Yokohama.

145
00:14:25,919 --> 00:14:28,991
I can't believe it yet, Julie.
Imagine them picking me.

146
00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:32,132
You're able, Roger.
You have ability.

147
00:14:32,133 --> 00:14:33,733
Anybody can see that.

148
00:14:35,319 --> 00:14:37,037
You're going, hm?

149
