I knew you'd want me
to take the job, sure.

158
00:15:01,954 --> 00:15:04,154
But, Julie...

159
00:15:04,419 --> 00:15:05,874
let's get married.

160
00:15:07,439 --> 00:15:09,716
Let's get married right away, tonight.

161
00:15:10,439 --> 00:15:13,395
I'll be able to send for you in three months.
I'll have the money then.

162
00:15:13,999 --> 00:15:17,755
Three months?
Why the rush to get married now?

163
00:15:19,179 --> 00:15:22,100
Well, do you think I'm going to let
a funny little redhead

164
00:15:22,101 --> 00:15:23,701
like you run around loose here?

165
00:15:23,819 --> 00:15:25,949
