184
00:17:02,099 --> 00:17:05,091
- Well, good bye, Applejack.
- Good bye, boy.

185
00:17:05,299 --> 00:17:07,688
- Keep an eye on Julie for me.
- I sure will, boy.

186
00:17:08,379 --> 00:17:10,500
So long, Dot.
Take good care of her.

187
00:17:10,501 --> 00:17:11,894
I will.

188
00:17:12,595 --> 00:17:13,695
Good bye.

189
00:17:15,739 --> 00:17:17,297
Good bye, darling.

190
00:17:18,539 --> 00:17:19,938
Excuse me a minute.

191
00:17:20,339 --> 00:17:22,170
-Wait for me.
-All right.

192
00:17:23,219 --> 00:17:25,175
Oh, Roger, I can't say good bye.

193
00:17:25,299 --> 00:17:27,017
Here you are, sir.

194
00:17:30,099 --> 00:17:31,327
Thank you.

195
00:17:31,659 --> 00:17:34,776
It's not good bye, darling.
It's just see you later.

196
