Mrs. Adams!
Sounds strange.

201
00:17:49,819 --> 00:17:52,458
Not strange.
It sounds great.

202
00:17:53,019 --> 00:17:55,328
- Does sound great, doesn't it
- Yes, darling.

203
00:18:04,299 --> 00:18:06,333
There's something about a train.

204
00:18:06,334 --> 00:18:10,700
I don't know whether it's the way
it looks or the way it smells, or what it is.

205
00:18:10,701 --> 00:18:13,358
It always makes me feel
I want to be off somewhere.

206
00:18:13,699 --> 00:18:17,533
I know, darling. I always feel
the same way.

207
00:18:18,059 --> 00:18:21,415
Oh, Roger,
I wish this was our honeymoon.

208
00:18:21,539 --> 00:18:23,416
Oh, I do too, darling.

209
00:18:30,579 --> 00:18:32,535
Promise me something, will you?

210
00:18:34,219 --> 00:18:36,289
