when I'm being highly romantic.

236
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,554
Nothing's too good for my little wife.

237
00:22:05,555 --> 00:22:07,155
Come on and see it.

238
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:10,891
- How do you like that?
- It's beautiful.

239
00:22:11,939 --> 00:22:13,736
